This is my Chat Server Java Source Code for the Weeby.co application.

Please Use command "telnet 54.183.164.84 8080" from terminal to access the Chat Room

Enjoy your chatting time!

To compile and run the server locally, please follow the below steps:

1. Download jdk 1.7 or above from oracle.
2. Install jdk, please refer the related documentation.
3. Change your current directory to the one contains the *.java files.
4. Run command "javac WeebyChatServer.java".
5. Run command "java WeebyChatServer" to use Default 8080 port.
6. Or run command "java WeebyChatServer port#" to indicate the port # you want to use.
7. To terminate the application, use Ctrl + C.